{"levelId":"forest-01","chapterId":"forest-01","worldId":"forest","title":"森林入口：发现脚印","rewards":{"growthPoints":5},"scenes":[{"sceneId":"gate","background":"assets/scenes/forest.webp","lines":[{"type":"narration","text":"星门把小小探险家送到森林入口。阳光穿过树叶，地上留下了一串圆圆的脚印。","character":"narrator"},{"type":"dialogue","text":"这里有树、有叶，还有一条小路。脚印会通向哪里？","character":"hero","position":"left"},{"type":"activity","activityType":"scan","prompt":"找出通往森林深处的脚印。","character":"forest_guide","position":"right","actions":[{"label":"观察圆脚印","feedback":"脚印通向一棵大树。"},{"label":"看看树叶路牌","feedback":"叶子轻轻摇动，指向溪边。"}]},{"type":"dialogue","text":"认识‘森’字，就像看见很多树站在一起。","character":"forest_guide","position":"right"}]}]}
